# Generate Playground
- The function should have a page parameter so only one page is loaded depending of the settings (ie: at the start of the application to avoid too many elements loaded, or when loading another page)
- Ordering the results by "order" should be done when querying it, not afterward through a sort function, allowing to order albums, groups and stickers and not only stickers
- Assign a theme through css rather than attribute ? Todo later ?
- Alt to links in my-sticker tags
- When selecting if a group should be row or column (other than with even or odd), add margin-top:2px or margin-left:2px depending of it

