# Resources
- Custom tags/elements : https://matthewjamestaylor.com/custom-tags?utm_content=cmp-true
    - Must contains an hyphen (\<my-element>)
    - Cannot be self closed (like \<img \/>) but can be empty (like \<p>\<\/p>)
    - Can contains custom attributes not relying on "data-" prefix, and can contains boolean attributes
- IDB docs :
    - https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/IndexedDB_API/Using_IndexedDB
    - https://www.w3docs.com/learn-javascript/javascript-indexeddb.html
    - https://www.w3.org/TR/IndexedDB/
    - https://javascript.info/indexeddb
- Custom class :
    - https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_components/Using_custom_elements
    - https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/custom-elements.html#custom-element-conformance
- Events :
    - https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Events
